Custom Configuration Framework (custom-conf)
============================================
Package: custom-conf-docker

This package provides standard configuration of the Docker Engine (daemon).

In particular, it addresses standard configuration of:
 - non-conflicting default network segment (<-> 'docker0' bridge)
 - consistent user namespaces
 - firewall rules (<-> 'custom-conf-iptables' package)
 - IPv6 (NAT) support (<-> 'docker1' bridge)
 - syslog integration (<-> 'custom-conf-rsyslog' package)

